data.description: Sophisticated, contemporary custom home on ¾ acre lot with swim spa. Room for a pool (estimate avail). Completely updated with an open floor plan, tons of light, & desert views. Gated community. Three bdrm/2.5 bath house, 2,830 SF, plus casita with 3/4 bath, 238 SF=3,068 SF total. Office could be 4th bdrm. Chef's kitchen with island, Bosch appliances and custom pantry/appliance garage. Integrated spaces include the living room, family room, dining room, breakfast area plus both counter and island seating in kitchen. Expansive primary suite with gorgeous recently remodeled bathroom and custom closet. All other bathrooms are updated and bdrms have walk-in closets. Large laundry room with extra counter space and second refrigerator. Sleek Italian porcelain tile flooring throughout.
